{
  "stem": "14867.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if they didn't tear us apart-- the only thing is I stood up to her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't get scared, show her any fear.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that was the main thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if somebody says-- you just laugh it off and go on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And don't tell me, could I do it now?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't even know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, in this kind of situation, you do things that you don't believe you could do it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I must tell you, when I talk to you, I say to myself I make up stories, because I don't know how you did it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My sister went to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I never mentioned it to you-- when the Nazis came, she went to work in a kitchen in the Gestapo, because she believed this is the safest thing.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Most girls would run away from the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She felt, if she goes to the Gestapo and asks for work, and has her papers, nobody will tell her-- will suspect that she's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It happened so that she was right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She even brought us some bread and potatoes from there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They gave it to her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now, it's true that she was always a very brave girl.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this is more than bravery.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you really did things that you couldn't possibly do it now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't even-- some day, I said to David, am I-- am I really telling the truth?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't even understand how we did it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even my mother who was so brave-- I never knew my mother is such a brave woman, because I never had the circumstances to see her.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She had everything she wanted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was highly respected.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's how I saw my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
